Name: Jackal
Fate: Bombed off Mersa Matruh on 11 May 1942 and scuttled by Jervis following day

Name: Jaguar
Fate: Torpedoed by German U-boat U.652 off Sollum, 26 March 1942

Name: Juno(ex-Jamaica)
Fate: Bombed and sunk south of Crete, 21 May 1941

Name: Janus
Fate: Torpedoed and sunk off Anzio by German aircraft, 23 January 1944
